## Risks and Mitigations
- **Groq outage/degradation:** Retry with backoff, clear user message, optional fallback to Ollama if available
- **API key expiry/revocation:** Fail-fast at startup with rotation guidance
- **Rate limiting during testing:** Add delay between regression queries
- **Answer quality regression vs Llama 3.2:** Regression test set, models architecturally equivalent
- **Unexpected token cost spike:** Monitor Groq console, add input length guard
- **.env key accidentally committed:** Ensure .gitignore correct before first commit
